To pass a single argument from a template, use the `fn` helper: `(fn this.task.perform argument)`. The `fn` helper partially applies the argument so that when the event fires, the task receives the correct value. From JavaScript, call `this.loadMatchDetail.perform('match-007')` directly.

```gjs
